  "detailed_description": "<h1>Recent Updates</h1><p>U.I. updates that are visually more in-line with the overall \"RR\" theme.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160800/extras/60836628fb81f69ef92f8098d3c27a2f.avif?t=1571287279\" width=576 height=324 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>PARKOUR MECHANICS, COLOR SWITCHING AND DISCO DANCING FUSED TO CREATE AN ADDICTING NEW SPIN ON THE ENDLESS RUNNING GENRE!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160800/extras/d4e17b73f73a64c8475323a29e90d59e.avif?t=1571287279\" width=576 height=324 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>80s cyberpunk themed synthwave tracks composed by an award winning music producer.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Standard Mode: Hone your skills and complete the game's Standard Mode to unlock the more challenging Panic Mode.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Panic Mode: Increased intensity, speed and music variation: Completing this mode requires masterful precision.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Character Customization: Collect spectrum coins with each run to unlock and equip groovy skins. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Disco Dancing: With each successful run, you're rewarded with a Disco Dance celebration.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160800/extras/2fa5ea95827d06548392505434079bc8.poster.avif?t=1571287279\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160800/extras/2fa5ea95827d06548392505434079bc8.webm?t=1571287279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160800/extras/2fa5ea95827d06548392505434079bc8.mp4?t=1571287279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "PARKOUR MECHANICS, COLOR SWITCHING AND DISCO DANCING FUSED TO CREATE AN ADDICTING NEW SPIN ON THE ENDLESS RUNNING GENRE!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160800/extras/d4e17b73f73a64c8475323a29e90d59e.avif?t=1571287279\" width=576 height=324 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>80s cyberpunk themed synthwave tracks composed by an award winning music producer.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Standard Mode: Hone your skills and complete the game's Standard Mode to unlock the more challenging Panic Mode.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Panic Mode: Increased intensity, speed and music variation: Completing this mode requires masterful precision.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Character Customization: Collect spectrum coins with each run to unlock and equip groovy skins. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Disco Dancing: With each successful run, you're rewarded with a Disco Dance celebration.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160800/extras/2fa5ea95827d06548392505434079bc8.poster.avif?t=1571287279\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160800/extras/2fa5ea95827d06548392505434079bc8.webm?t=1571287279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160800/extras/2fa5ea95827d06548392505434079bc8.mp4?t=1571287279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
